Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:08.36,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Once there was a man who obtained everything,\Nthe legendary Pirate King Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:12.91,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,His last words before he was executed inspired people to sail the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:14.63,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,All my wealth and treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.27,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,It can be yours if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.42,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,Search for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:19.83,Gold,Roger,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything in that one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.82,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,People now set sail in search of romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.40,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The world has entered a Great Age of Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:39.75,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,All pirates who seek One Piece\Nstrive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:51.27,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean\Nwas the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:57.57,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has killed\Nthe dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:03.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the boy who ate the Gomu Gomu Fruit\Nand became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nare going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:11.27,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:18.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Two years have passed since the great war at Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:23.59,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the Straw Hats regrouped at their promised meeting place, the Sabaody Archipelago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.32,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,before setting course for their next stage - The New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:31.09,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They had reached Fishman Island, located\Nten thousand meters under the sea, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:36.61,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,they were attacked by a group calling themselves the New Fishman Pirates, and were scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:42.95,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others were drowning, but the mermaids saved them and took them to Caimie's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.25,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.83,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!  Isn't there anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anyone!  I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.71,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Give Sanji blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.48,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Please!  Give him blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.31,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,My companion is about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.17,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anyone out there have blood type S, Rh negative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:19.44,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,We're running out of time!\NPlease give him a blood transfusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.34,Main,Them,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.54,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Sanji-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.50,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,It's very difficult for a human\N to get a blood transfusion on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.46,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure Luffy-chin and the others will keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:49.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  Even though we're searching so hard, we still can't find anyone who'll give him a transfusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:52.40,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up!  There must be somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.20,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.56,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:02.69,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy!  There are humans over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:15.46,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,This barrel washed ashore with Caimie's friends.\NI wonder what's inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.33,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Alcohol?  Treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:21.59,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows... It's sealed pretty tight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:24.80,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?  Should we secretly open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.55,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.22,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.93,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  I see you've come prepared, Ishilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:47.28,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!  Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:47.95,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.83,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:54.83,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.16,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the house of one of my friends from the port town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.54,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-chin, you'd lost\Nmost of the blood in your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:06.67,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we were able to find\Na donor with the same blood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:08.26,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,I see... My blood, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.31,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.10,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't get up so suddenly!  Stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:21.11,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But really, why did the fishmen refuse to give him blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:25.82,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We ran all over town,\Nbut we couldn't find any humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.45,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly thought it was hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.12,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping me, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:35.33,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.57,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Where was I, and what was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.83,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,I can almost recall it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.71,Main,Usopp & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't recall it! { def: is the initial "ha!" part of the phrase or just a shout? } {Gil: Sounds just like a shout to me. Retimed line to not include the shout.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.92,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,If you get another nosebleed, you'll be beyond saving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:53.30,Main,Usopp & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!  Sanji, let me introduce\Nthe blood donors we met at the bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.53,Main,Usopp & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You really should thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:03.56,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I was given blood by... a delicate lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.92,Thoughts,Totally hot and totally not imaginary woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:15.25,Thoughts,Totally hot and totally not imaginary woman,0000,0000,0000,,We humans need to help each other out in times of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:21.29,Main,Oh god no,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.09,Main,Oh god no,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, we'll gladly give you more, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.43,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you've recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.81,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, thank them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:46.44,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.  Let me see your right arm for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.32,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,A poison reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.41,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,That wound is poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, while I was fighting the fishmen earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.54,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I did feel a slight sting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:06.50,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,And you're completely fine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.00,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, show me your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.30,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,This poison is lethal!  Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:13.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.93,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:21.64,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's body must have developed antitoxins, and repelled the poison without us noticing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:25.52,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been exposed to\Nlarge amounts of poison before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Poison, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:35.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I was almost killed by poison back in Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.83,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Almost killed?\NIs that really something to laugh about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The swordsman with the octopus-legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He withstood my attack, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.64,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,He was pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:02.85,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,That came from the cove.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.27,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,Those mermaids sure are noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:08.81,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:12.03,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are both out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.85,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,And I carelessly ended up poisoning Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.69,Main,Hyouzou,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be real bad if he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.70,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,That scream was from Ishilly and the others, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.50,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.71,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.11,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I heard them over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.85,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:35.22,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I heard them talking about opening a barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.61,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin, and all of you,\Ncome over here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.37,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I'd like you to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:49.15,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,The manager of the Mermaid Café.  She let us borrow the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.07,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,This is Madame Shyarly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.40,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.11,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Is the blond boy alright now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:59.30,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.12,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,But Madame,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.12,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,since you're so beautiful\Nyou should stay out of his room for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.39,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the fact that we're in the back rooms\Nof the Mermaid Café...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.25,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret from Sanji-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.54,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.55,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Because if he finds out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.34,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be in trouble again,\Nor so his doctor, Chopper-chin, says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:20.68,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,That's an odd prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.26,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Huge mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.89,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Madame Shyarly, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.23,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.48,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:31.92,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that, Straw Hat Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.40,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.15,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,That's a crystal ball.  It's used for fortune-telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:40.66,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Madame is famous for\Nmaking predictions here on Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.62,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,I've quit fortune-telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:52.50,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,It's better not to know the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.54,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So, do mermaids poop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.97,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddaya mean, "so"?!\NThat has nothing to do with fortune-telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:02.30,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,You vulgar boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.85,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to her, Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.89,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:08.51,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Caimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.98,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to take the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.15,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Give your friends a tour of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.02,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.03,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,You've been working really hard, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.86,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.46,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, we haven't gotten a single human pirate customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.83,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,This will be good for business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:30.50,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,The girls from the cove will be coming here soon, so we've got more than enough staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.83,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,More than enough starfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.31,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:37.30,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to hurry and give Pappagg his clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.30,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That's one weird way to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:43.01,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,He must be starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.33,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:49.27,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,If you mean Monsieur Pappagg, he met an old friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.98,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them are hanging out in the café right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.19,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,In the café?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.93,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,An old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.08,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mention this earlier but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.12,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Back when the Madame was still a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.54,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,she said that lots of pirates\Nwould be coming to the island soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:14.54,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,And then the Great Age of Pirates began the following year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.42,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.03,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,It'd take way too long if I told you all the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:24.13,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,but a while back she also predicted\Nthe war at Marineford and the death of Whitebeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.97,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.51,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's predicted so many bad things, it sounds like she's gotten tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.10,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.60,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where's Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.35,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking after Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.40,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin, Usopp-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:38.57,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:44.49,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,This is the main street on Coral Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:48.91,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  This is the entrance to the Mermaid Café!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:54.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I sure am hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.79,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a café!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.52,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,We have food here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:59.46,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Like cake and fruits of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.96,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,How about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:04.84,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Merfolk don't eat meat or fish, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:08.64,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,the menu consists of Seaweed Brûlée, Algae Tart, Kelp Soufflé...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.85,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Is any of that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.81,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,But we do have meat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.73,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:17.83,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Shellfish meat, Scallop Sandwich, Freshwater Clam Pizza{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Shellfish meat doesn't count!  Don't insult meat like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.90,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get going.  To the Mermaid Café.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.32,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  Pappagg's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.57,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!  Don't look down on meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.58,Main,Maameidzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.99,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Resting my tired bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.83,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.89,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.10,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Brook-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.79,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  Why, if it isn't Luffy-san and Usopp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:03.82,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,And Caimie-san, it has been far too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.51,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,So, to get right to the point, may I see your panti{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.86,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,She's a mermaid, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.78,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Straw!  Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.94,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I've really missed you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.58,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Long time, no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.79,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,So you were with Pappagg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:22.54,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  I never thought I would be rescued by Pappagg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.80,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:29.05,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right!  I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.76,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to perfect an idea for a new design down at the cove,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:36.73,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,when Bones here just came drifting down the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:39.92,Flashbacks,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:40.84,Flashbacks,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bones?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.78,Main,Maameidzu,0000,0000,0000,,Please come again, Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.28,Main,Maameidzu,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like we've been living a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:53.74,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely comin' back, beautiful mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.91,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.10,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I need to loosen my bones a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:02.33,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!  But if I were to loosen my bones, I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:07.42,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind dying right now!  Though I already am dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.84,Main,Maameidzu,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.76,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,They've just been in a café,\Nyet the tension is already this high?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.13,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!  What's it like in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.89,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Now, wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.06,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're leaving today, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:24.90,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you're interested,\Nbut later you can all go to the Mermaid Café together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:29.86,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to take Bones on a tour of my mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:34.61,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!  Do you like the meat of sea beasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.58,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You have meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:42.33,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,You think a wild man such as myself\Nwould be satisfied with seashells and seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:45.75,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,My diet consists of\Nthe meat of the very fiercest sea beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.71,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Pappagg, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.42,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your clams for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.80,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!  Caimie's delicious clams!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.47,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't those just shellfish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:55.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.31,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:04.94,Flashbacks,Oh god no,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:11.95,Main,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.66,Flashbacks,Oh god no,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.37,Main,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the others are doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:27.16,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Merfolk don't eat meat and fish, but fishmen do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:30.09,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not like there isn't any of it on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:31.97,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  That's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.99,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.26,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.60,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Easy does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.77,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.14,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.19,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a ghost on the wanted list?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.57,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from the ghost ship we met on the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.20,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You met him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:17:01.04,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,He's some kind of undersea robber who\Nthe country has been hunting down for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.46,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,But let's talk about that later.  For now, get onboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:22.42,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken used to send a love letter to the Mermaid Princess of Ryuuguu Kingdom every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:29.44,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually he went from letters to packages,\N and then threats and demands for her to marry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.15,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,This is so fluffy!  It feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.28,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,This truly feels like paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.47,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:37.54,Main,Luffy & Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.54,0:17:38.47,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:44.04,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,When the situation reached that point,\Nthe princess was terrified...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.68,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,and the country could no longer ignore it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:51.72,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!  The princess' father, King Neptune, got upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:57.47,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,and the three princes you met earlier mobilized the army to chase after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.47,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,but they couldn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:03.33,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Caimie... Caimie... I was just about to explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:07.83,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, King Neptune the Sea God,\Nwho rules this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:11.80,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,has four children including the Mermaid Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:17.71,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,The Mermaid Princess is the youngest, and her\Nbig brothers are the three princes you met earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:19.88,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, Caimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:23.08,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but something bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:29.48,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Vander Decken that cursed pirate from several hundred years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:30.79,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:35.39,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, legends are often\Nexaggerations of exaggerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.25,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that he did exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:46.97,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,but the Vander Decken from the legend was just a man who reached this island and lived in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:52.56,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,So, the ship you encountered\Nwas probably the real Flying Dutchman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.03,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,but the captain was just his descendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:57.98,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Va{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.98,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,Vander Decken the ninth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.52,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  His descendant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:08.43,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's how it is?  So he wasn't a ghost after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:13.46,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Being only bones, and thinking I had met a real ghost, I was starting to feel more dead than alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.63,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.\NIf nothing else, I am truly happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.38,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Caimie... Caimie... Caimie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:25.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!  Now that I look closely, there are\Nso many different kinds of merfolk and fishmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:29.18,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,There are old lady mermaids down there too!\NThey're just like old Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.82,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!  Those are babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:36.23,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Their father is a fishman,\Nbut his kids are both merfolk and fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:44.32,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, if a fishman and a mermaid get married, they can have sons and daughters of either race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.41,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there are four possible outcomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.32,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why there are so many different types!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.00,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.55,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting on the high-speed current now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.49,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,This is so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.75,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.02,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the candy factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.89,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.\NWhy is there a pirate-flag on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:13.06,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that?  There's one at the bay\Nand at the entrance to the island too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:16.63,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island is currently\Nunder the protection of that pirate flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:21.87,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,It's the mark of the New World pirate\NCharlotte Linlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:25.53,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as Big Mam.  One of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.40,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Four Emperors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:34.78,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Before the war, this island was protected from pirates by Whitebeard's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:36.96,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Big Mam is watching over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.75,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:43.69,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, we have to give her\Nlarge amounts of candy every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:46.22,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the factory is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.97,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:50.66,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,If we're not protected by someone great like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.60,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,the country would never survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It would become too dangerous here, since it's like the pirates' highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:02.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But if this Big Mam is protecting you in old man Whitebeard's place, she must be nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:07.44,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say... At least Whitebeard never asked for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:11.08,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Big Mam just thinks of it like business?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:15.39,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mam, huh?  One of the Four Emperors,\Njust like Shanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.08,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll meet her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.56,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,Look up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:23.03,Main,Pappagg,0000,0000,0000,,We have reached the city of celebrities,\NFishverly Hills!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:28.47,Main,Caimie,0000,0000,0000,,That huge building right in front of us\Nis Pappagg's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.44,Main,They,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That?!  But he's just a starfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.06,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.28,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that the Madame from the Mermaid Café?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.94,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Madame Shyarly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:48.62,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:51.91,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act quickly, something terrible will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.33,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Madame... What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.00,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Go look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:02.05,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate-boy wearing a straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.51,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Chase him out of the kingdom, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:08.72,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Is this another prediction?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.01,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't intend to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:16.78,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,but I felt something from him, and ended up taking a peek...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:17.85,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,at his future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:22.36,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!  What did you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.73,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Madame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.86,Main,Mermaid,0000,0000,0000,,Shyarly?!  Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.11,Main,Fishman,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.53,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Let it be wrong!  Please, let my prediction be wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:51.82,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,The human with the straw hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.41,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.14,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,By his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.56,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,Fishman Island will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:04.86,Main,Shyarly,0000,0000,0000,,be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.95,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The brightly shining Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:13.53,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Even here, there is darkness born from history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:16.89,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Individuals who loathe humans,\Nand who bare their fangs for the sake of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.89,0:23:19.71,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They make their move, deep underneath the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.58,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Luffy and the others are having fun in Pappagg's store,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.52,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,when King Neptune, the ruler of Fishman Island,\Nappears before them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:27.84,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.84,0:23:29.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Fishman Island
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.34,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Neptune the Sea God!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:32.62,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
